00:00:00.600 --> 00:00:05.100
<v Hitomi>Hello everyone! I'm Hitomi Takamatsu from =LOVE.
<v Hana>I'm Hana Oba!

NOTE Nametags use PAIRING, repositioned slightly to match the members
00:00:00.800 --> 00:00:04.000 line:80% position:25% align:center
<c.nametag>=LOVE
Hitomi Takamatsu</c>

00:00:00.800 --> 00:00:04.000 line:80% position:75% align:center
<c.nametag>=LOVE
Hana Oba</c>

00:00:05.800 --> 00:00:09.000
- It's raining!
- Oh, it's starting to rain! Just a drizzle.

00:00:09.500 --> 00:00:15.500
- It's been a while since we did a video with just us two.
- Yeah, the last time was the home-cooked meal battle.

NOTE Previous video thumbnail, standalone cue (COVERING)
00:00:13.500 --> 00:00:16.000 line:15% position:50% align:center
<c.title>[Previous Video: Home-cooked Meal Battle]</c>

00:00:16.800 --> 00:00:20.500
Today, we're not doing a cooking battle,
we're going shopping!

00:00:20.600 --> 00:00:23.000
Yay! Let's go on a shopping spree!

00:00:24.000 --> 00:00:29.500
- So, the store for today is...
- Ta-da! ZARA in Shibuya!

00:00:30.000 --> 00:00:34.500
- We're finally here. You really love ZARA, Hana.
- I do, I love it.

00:00:34.500 --> 00:00:38.200
- I always picture you wearing ZARA clothes. Guide me.
- It's super spacious in here.

00:00:38.200 --> 00:00:40.500
I'm sure they have everything.

00:00:40.500 --> 00:00:43.500
Today, we have a budget of 30,000 yen for shopping!

00:00:44.200 --> 00:00:47.500
- Wow, I'm so happy! We can buy so much.
- It feels like a real treat.

00:00:47.800 --> 00:00:53.000
The rule is, we have to buy a full outfit
for ourselves...

00:00:53.000 --> 00:00:58.500
- Plus one item that we think would suit each other.
- All under a total of 30,000 yen!

00:00:59.800 --> 00:01:03.500
- I wonder if we can shop smartly?
- Let's do our best! It'll be fun.

00:01:04.200 --> 00:01:07.500
- Let's go then!
- Let's go!

00:01:10.000 --> 00:01:13.500
- We're done shopping!
- We're done!

00:01:15.800 --> 00:01:19.500
- I had such a hard time deciding!
- I was actually pretty fast.

00:01:19.500 --> 00:01:23.500
- Yeah, you made up your mind so quickly!
- You're done already?

00:01:24.000 --> 00:01:28.000
- But you completely disappeared on me.
- I was around, everywhere.

00:01:28.500 --> 00:01:32.000
- We didn't cross paths at all.
- I'm just glad we managed to buy everything.

00:01:34.000 --> 00:01:38.000
- Can I show mine first?
- I spent exactly 30,000 yen!

NOTE Intro telop simplified and positioned to avoid stacking
00:01:34.000 --> 00:01:37.000 line:15% align:center
<c.title>[Hitomi Takamatsu's Purchases]</c>

00:01:38.500 --> 00:01:42.500
- That's amazing!
- And I even managed to get a bag and shoes.

00:01:43.000 --> 00:01:46.000
- Really? That's incredible!
- Let's start with the main item.

00:01:46.500 --> 00:01:50.000
Ta-da! This top!

NOTE Item box handled as COVERING standalone cue in top right corner to preserve screen budget
00:01:48.000 --> 00:01:51.500 line:15% position:75% align:start
<c.item-box>Striped Bow Knit Top (S)
¥4,390</c>

00:01:51.500 --> 00:01:56.500
- You know what, I actually picked that for you too!
- You chose this?!

00:01:56.500 --> 00:02:00.000
When we passed by each other, I saw you holding it.

00:02:00.500 --> 00:02:04.500
I was thinking how perfect this top would look on you.

00:02:04.500 --> 00:02:09.500
You don't wear stripes very often,
so I wanted you to try it.

00:02:10.500 --> 00:02:14.000
And then you ended up picking it yourself!

00:02:14.500 --> 00:02:17.500
- Incredible, right? So I definitely had to get it.
- It has a nice marine vibe to it.

00:02:17.500 --> 00:02:22.000
Our teacher said that this summer's theme is marine.

00:02:22.500 --> 00:02:28.000
- This was 4,390 yen with tax.
- I got it in size S, the smallest one.

00:02:30.000 --> 00:02:33.500
- I'm glad you got it.
- Next, denim pants!

00:02:33.500 --> 00:02:37.000
I've been really into denim lately.

00:02:37.500 --> 00:02:40.500
Ta-da! Isn't it so cute?

00:02:37.500 --> 00:02:41.000 line:15% position:75% align:start
<c.item-box>TRF Mid-Rise Foldover Denim (S)
¥7,990</c>

00:02:41.500 --> 00:02:47.000
- I intentionally went for distressed jeans.
- I think they'll suit you.

00:02:47.500 --> 00:02:51.000
I rarely own pants with holes in them,
so I wanted to buy one.

00:02:51.000 --> 00:02:55.500
- And this part is really stylish. You'd like this, right?
- Yeah, I like it.

00:02:56.500 --> 00:03:00.000
At first, I thought the smallest size would be best.

00:03:00.000 --> 00:03:04.500
- But then I saw they had a size 32, the smallest!
- So lucky!

00:03:05.000 --> 00:03:08.500
- That's why I grabbed this right away.
- It was 7,990 yen.

00:03:09.000 --> 00:03:13.500
It looks clean and neat at a glance,
but the bottom has ripped details.

00:03:14.000 --> 00:03:18.000
- It feels very "me."
- I totally get that.

00:03:18.500 --> 00:03:22.500
To go with these two items...
I got a matching bag!

00:03:23.000 --> 00:03:26.500
- Very marine.
- With an outfit like this, the bag has to be red!

00:03:29.500 --> 00:03:33.000 line:15% position:75% align:start
<c.item-box>Long Shoulder Bag
¥5,290</c>

00:03:30.500 --> 00:03:35.000
This was 5,290 yen. Cute, isn't it?

00:03:35.500 --> 00:03:39.000
- How are you so good at shopping?
- Am I? I'm so glad.

00:03:39.500 --> 00:03:43.000
But I still had budget left, so I bought sandals too!

00:03:44.000 --> 00:03:49.000
- Wow, you made a complete outfit.
- I know, these thick-soled sandals are so cute.

00:03:49.500 --> 00:03:54.000
Aren't they? I think I'll be wearing these
all the time this summer.

00:03:59.000 --> 00:04:02.500 line:15% position:75% align:start
<c.item-box>Satin Bow Platform Sandals (40)
¥6,590</c>

00:04:00.000 --> 00:04:04.000
It was 6,590 yen. The size is... 40!

00:04:04.500 --> 00:04:09.500
- That's huge.
- My feet are really big, like 25 cm.

00:04:09.500 --> 00:04:14.000
If it's not a 40, it won't fit me.
It has to be 40, 25, or LL.

00:04:18.500 --> 00:04:22.500
- So, I bought these 4 items!
- The total price is... here!

00:04:22.500 --> 00:04:27.500
30,250 yen! You're such a good shopper!

NOTE Slight sequencing so the telop doesn't collide with the dialogue text
00:04:23.000 --> 00:04:27.000 line:15% align:center
<c.title>TOTAL: ¥30,250
(Includes the item for Hana)</c>

00:04:28.000 --> 00:04:32.000
- Yay! I'm so satisfied.
- You gathered a lot of great stuff.

00:04:34.000 --> 00:04:37.000
Alright, now it's my turn!

00:04:34.500 --> 00:04:37.500 line:15% align:center
<c.title>[Hana Oba's Purchases]</c>

00:04:37.500 --> 00:04:41.500
- Go ahead.
- I wanted this jacket right from the start!

00:04:44.000 --> 00:04:47.500
- I just knew you'd pick that!
- The moment I saw this, I thought, "This is it!"

00:04:48.000 --> 00:04:52.500
- ZARA sells a lot of Napoleon jackets.
- Oh, really?

00:04:53.000 --> 00:04:57.500
They had various kinds, and I thought
this one was adorable, so I grabbed it.

00:04:58.500 --> 00:05:02.000 line:15% position:75% align:start
<c.item-box>Z1975 Peplum Jacket (S)
¥10,990</c>

00:04:58.500 --> 00:05:05.500
- It's a size S... and it cost 10,990 yen.
- Ten thousand yen!

00:05:06.000 --> 00:05:10.500
- You're rich!
- It has a beautiful shape, fits perfectly.

00:05:11.000 --> 00:05:15.000
- I actually tried it on too.
- It looked so cute when I wore it, so I chose it.

00:05:16.500 --> 00:05:21.000
Next, to pair with it,
I got this semi-sheer polka dot top.

00:05:21.500 --> 00:05:25.500
It would look cute worn underneath,
especially with the sleeves peeking out.

00:05:28.500 --> 00:05:32.000 line:15% position:75% align:start
<c.item-box>Polka Dot Semi-Sheer Knit Top (XS)
¥5,290</c>

00:05:28.000 --> 00:05:33.500
- This is a size XS, for 5,290 yen.
- It's cute, slightly see-through.

00:05:35.500 --> 00:05:40.000
- I can wear it with a camisole.
- I thought about buying another layer if I had enough...

00:05:40.500 --> 00:05:43.000
And luckily I did! It looks like a corset.

00:05:44.000 --> 00:05:48.000
- I want to layer them together. Do you think it'll fit?
- Cute! Wow, now I'm worried it won't fit.

00:05:49.500 --> 00:05:53.000
- Wait, is it going to fit being this small?
- What size is it anyway? M!

00:05:54.000 --> 00:05:58.000
- It'll definitely fit!
- If you can't fit into it, who could?

00:05:59.000 --> 00:06:05.000
- You're an idol, of course it'll fit. If it doesn't... oh well.
- Don't give up on it!

00:06:06.500 --> 00:06:10.000 line:15% position:75% align:start
<c.item-box>Lace Trim Corset Top (M)
¥4,390</c>

00:06:07.000 --> 00:06:11.000
It's size M, for 4,390 yen.

00:06:11.500 --> 00:06:16.000
- Then for pants, these shorts!
- Cute!

00:06:16.000 --> 00:06:20.000
The top has long sleeves,
so I wanted to keep the bottoms short.

00:06:20.500 --> 00:06:25.000
I like the color brown, and it comes with
a brown belt too, so it's perfect.

00:06:27.500 --> 00:06:31.000 line:15% position:75% align:start
<c.item-box>High-Rise Bermuda Shorts with Belt (XS)
¥5,290</c>

00:06:27.500 --> 00:06:31.500
It's size XS, 5,290 yen.

00:06:31.500 --> 00:06:35.500
- I wonder what the total is?
- Is it within the budget? I'll show it on screen.

00:06:37.000 --> 00:06:41.000 line:15% align:center
<c.title>TOTAL: ¥30,864 (Before Tax)</c>

00:06:38.000 --> 00:06:45.000
- I calculated the prices before tax...
- Oh, before tax.

00:06:41.500 --> 00:06:46.000 line:15% align:center
<c.title>TOTAL: ¥33,950 (With Tax)</c>

00:06:46.000 --> 00:06:49.000
- With tax, it comes to this much...
- Waaaa!

00:06:49.500 --> 00:06:54.000
By the way, the total for both of you
with tax included is 64,200 yen.

00:06:55.000 --> 00:06:59.000
- That means someone went over budget...
- It's you who went over!

00:06:59.500 --> 00:07:02.000
Wait, me?!

00:07:03.000 --> 00:07:07.500
Also, today we didn't just shop for ourselves,
we picked out an item for each other too.

00:07:08.500 --> 00:07:12.500
- I had such a hard time deciding!
- Even though I had already set my mind on one.

00:07:13.000 --> 00:07:18.000
- Because of that, I had to search all over again!
- If we hadn't crossed paths, it would've been bad.

00:07:18.500 --> 00:07:25.000
- This is what I ended up getting.
- Luckily they had two of the bags, so we're good.

00:07:28.000 --> 00:07:34.000
I picked clothes that I personally want to wear...
I mean, our fashion styles are different...

00:07:34.000 --> 00:07:39.500
I was just curious to see what you
would look like wearing my style.

00:07:40.000 --> 00:07:46.000
- You said this is what I'd usually pick, right?
- Yeah, it screams "Hitomi"!

00:07:46.500 --> 00:07:51.500
Wow, this is totally me!
I wear clothes like this all the time.

00:07:52.000 --> 00:07:59.000
- I love this kind of clothing too.
- But if I wore it, it'd look too normal, wouldn't it?

00:07:59.000 --> 00:08:07.500
- That's why I wanted you to wear my everyday style!
- I'm so happy, thank you!

00:08:18.000 --> 00:08:22.000 line:15% position:75% align:start
<c.item-box>Wavy Trim Knit Top (S)
¥5,990</c>

00:08:18.000 --> 00:08:22.500
- It's 5,990 yen for a size S.
- You're really good at picking things out.

00:08:26.500 --> 00:08:33.000
- And this still fits within the 30,000 yen budget, right?
- Yep! Thank you.

00:08:34.000 --> 00:08:38.500
- So, the item I chose for Hitomi is...
- What could it be?

00:08:38.500 --> 00:08:44.000
I picked something that's easy to wear daily,
and something that's totally my style.

00:08:44.000 --> 00:08:48.000
See, we thought of the exact same thing!
I'm glad we're on the same wavelength.

00:08:49.000 --> 00:08:54.000
- I chose this!
- Huh?! I'm so happy! It's so cute!

00:08:54.500 --> 00:08:59.000
- A Napoleon vest!
- Adorable, right? It'll definitely look great on you.

00:08:59.000 --> 00:09:03.500
- Perfect for the summer.
- Right? I'm sure you'll wear it a lot.

00:09:04.000 --> 00:09:08.500
- It really opens up a new side of me.
- Isn't it cute?

00:09:09.000 --> 00:09:14.000
- We can match, can't we? The black and white Napoleon duo!
- I can't wait to put it on.

00:09:16.500 --> 00:09:20.500 line:15% position:75% align:start
<c.item-box>Halter Neck Button Vest (S)
¥7,990</c>

00:09:16.500 --> 00:09:22.000
- It's size S, 7,990 yen.
- Wow, this is actually pretty expensive.

00:09:23.000 --> 00:09:29.000
Sorry about that. I was torn between
the 5,000 yen or the 7,000 yen one...

00:09:29.000 --> 00:09:34.000
- But I really wanted to see you wear this one.
- Thank you! I'll take good care of it.

00:09:34.500 --> 00:09:39.000
- Well then, let's go change!
- We'll start with the outfits we picked for ourselves.

00:09:39.500 --> 00:09:43.000
We're done changing!

00:09:46.500 --> 00:09:51.500
- What do you think?
- It's so cute! It looks amazing!

00:09:56.000 --> 10:00.000
- It suits you so well.
- You too, super cute!

10:00.000 --> 10:05.500
- Do you have a theme?
- The theme is... "Let's Go to France."

10:05.500 --> 10:11.000
Wait, I was thinking the exact same thing!
We're the France duo part two.

10:12.000 --> 10:17.500
Seriously, our outfits are very French.
Let's go to Paris!

10:19.000 --> 10:24.000
- Wow, your clothes actually fit!
- Thank goodness they did, I was so nervous earlier.

10:24.000 --> 10:29.000
- I'm glad the corset fit. Isn't it cute?
- Super cute! The size is absolutely perfect.

10:30.000 --> 10:35.000
- The pants fit too, even though I didn't try them on.
- It's adorable, and the jacket goes well with it.

10:38.000 --> 10:44.000
- I deliberately went for a layered look.
- Layered clothes look so good, don't they?

10:45.000 --> 10:50.000
- You're on a pro level, layering three pieces.
- It's so cute, I'll definitely wear it to work.

10:56.000 --> 11:00.500
- It'll become my favorite outfit.
- It's a huge success!

11:01.000 --> 11:06.000
- My shoes are cute too, right?
- It's perfect, down to the sandals.

11:08.500 --> 11:13.500
Even though there were neat, tailored
denim pants available...

11:13.500 --> 11:18.000
I still wanted to go for a casual vibe.

11:18.500 --> 11:23.000
- This is my summer style!
- Cute!

11:23.000 --> 11:27.500
My stomach is a little covered up,
but the style looks roughly like this.

11:28.000 --> 11:33.500
It's so nice, you look just like you usually do.
It really feels like your everyday clothes.

11:34.000 --> 11:39.000
We both managed to pick styles that match
our daily wear perfectly. Huge success!

11:49.000 --> 11:54.000
- Now let's change into the clothes we picked for each other!
- Let's do this! Let's go!

11:55.000 --> 12:00.000
We're done changing!

12:02.000 --> 12:06.500
Look at this, isn't it amazing?!
I was honestly surprised when I tried it on.

12:07.000 --> 12:12.500
It's so ruffled and bouncy! It's so cute!

12:14.000 --> 12:19.500
- I deliberately paired it with my denim from today...
- Wow, you look just like me!

12:20.000 --> 12:25.000
- It screams "Hitomi Takamatsu" style!
- So cute! It suits you perfectly.

12:26.000 --> 12:30.000
- I'll definitely wear this often. I want to buy the pants too.
- Whatever you wear, it always looks great on you.

12:35.000 --> 12:40.000
It looks like a mushroom, right?
But a very delicious-looking mushroom!

12:43.000 --> 12:48.000
Mine is cute too, you know! It looks great, right?

12:50.000 --> 12:55.000
Such a summer lady.
Reminds me of my baton twirling days.

12:55.000 --> 13:00.000
- I feel ready to spin a baton. Even though I rarely wear this stuff.
- It actually works really well for daily wear.

13:00.000 --> 13:05.000
- Especially paired with these pants.
- It really feels like we swapped clothes! Huge success!

13:16.000 --> 13:22.000
That's all for our ZARA shopping project today! Bye-bye!